{"tid":191072,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友係咪無當我係朋友，求解","createTime":"2017-04-07T14:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T15:55:33.000Z","uid":99569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c769a88445f3819cb5c8436ae58db6d0f5dbb237","tid":191072,"uid":99569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:31:55.000Z","msg":"我都係呻下咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實一直以黎我唔係真係無朋友，但係總覺得朋友都無正真當我係可以傾訴既人。<br />\n有時候成日FB見到自己啲朋友都會約我都熟既朋友出下街，傾下計咁。<br />\n但偏偏唔輪到我，根本就無揾過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟係咪同我相處既朋友覺得我好疏，唔岩陪伴？<br />\n定係注定左無朋友呢樣野.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9cb15a60c342729e3527cc1a260250ad971dd41","tid":191072,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:33:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eed7381b7a4ade33a62b977fe8c5be82e6f23dcf","tid":191072,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:35:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無搵過你就證明冇當你真正朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一次都無就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e597d6787c76d4c324e0fd5fd392afea6c6877e","tid":191072,"uid":99569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無搵過你就證明冇當你真正朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係平時都會食個飯開，出黎傾下計咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係唔揾我既情況愈來愈多..."},{"pid":"9961eb956ff304ce251435e372c58dae4562946e","tid":191072,"uid":99569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無搵過你就證明冇當你真正朋友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas